::DevilDuer::

DevilDuer grins, walking back to Diamond. "What can I say? Guess I'm 
just a great bot."

He turns the laser cutter he was holding to the lowest power 
setting. "This might hurt just a bit."

He takes hold of her arm, beginning to cut the wires off.


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, logomorph@h... wrote:
> Diamond::
> 
> "I don't need a medic, just need you to cut the wires and close the 
> small slit that they are sticking out of. It doesn't hurt.  But I'm 
> afriad the wires will get in the way."
> 
> She watched him get a few instruments. 
> 
> She smiled. "Yeah know. It's been a long time since any one's ever 
> talked to me nicely like you have. Thanks."
> 
> She didn't think that she really liked him yet, but at least, he 
was 
> intellegent, friendly, and most of all, not out to kill her.  At 
> least not yet.  She held her arm still for  him.
